          "grammarNote": "Aimer + infinitive = to like doing something: 'J'aime lire' (I like reading). Aimer bien softens aimer when talking about things (vs people): 'J'aime bien ce film'. Adorer is stronger: 'J'adore la musique'. For activities with faire, add 'de': 'J'aime faire du sport'."
